msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "FLAC (Free Lossless Audio Codec) Encoder"
msgstr "FLAC (Free Lossless Audio Codec) enkôder"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "FLAC stands for Free Lossless Audio Codec, an audio format similar to MP3, but lossless, meaning that audio is compressed in FLAC without any loss in quality. This is similar to how Zip works, except with FLAC you will get much better compression because it is designed specifically for audio, and you can play back compressed FLAC files in your favorite player (or your car or home stereo, see supported devices) just like you would an MP3 file.[CR][CR]FLAC stands out as the fastest and most widely supported lossless audio codec, and the only one that at once is non-proprietary, is unencumbered by patents, has an open-source reference implementation, has a well documented format and API, and has several other independent implementations."
msgstr "FLAC je skraćenica za Free Lossless Audio Codec, zvučni format sličan kao MP3, ali bez gubitaka, što znači da je zvuk kompresiran s FLAC-om bez gubitka kvalitete. To je slično kako Zip radi, osim s FLAC-om dobit ćete bolju kompresiju zato jer je dizajniran posebno za zvuk, i možete reporducirati kompresirane FLAC datoteke u vašem omiljenom reporduktoru (ili vašem autu ili kućnom stereo sustavu, pogledajte podržane uređaje) poput MP3 datoteka.[CR][CR]FLAC je najbrži i najraširenije podržani format kôdeka bez gubitka kvalitete, i jedni koji nije vlasnički, nije opterećen patentima, ima referentnu implementaciju otvorenog kôda, ima dobro dokumentiran format i API, te ima nekoliko drugih neovisnih implementacija."

msgctxt "#30000"
msgid "Compression level"
msgstr "Razina kompresije"

msgctxt "#30001"
msgid "FLAC uses a compression level parameter that varies from 0 (fastest) to 8 (slowest). The compressed files are always perfect, lossless representations of the original data. Although the compression process involves a tradeoff between speed and size, the decoding process is always quite fast and not dependent on the level of compression."
msgstr "FLAC koristi parametar razine kompresije koji varira od 0 (najbrže) do 8 (najsporije). Kompresirane datoteke su uvijek savršene, bez gubitka reprezentacije izvornih podataka. Iako proces kompresije uključuje kompromis između brzine i veličine, proces dekôdiranja uvijek je prilično brz i ne ovisi o razini kompresije."
